{
  "description": "User requests a tentative schedule for a new hybrid pilot course; the assistant gathers course, room, and faculty data, runs the optimizer, and delivers the schedule with an optional PDF report emailed to stakeholders.",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "system",
      "content": "You are AcademicSchedulerAI, an AI\u2011driven scheduling assistant for higher\u2011education institutions. Use the provided tools to fetch course, room, and faculty data, run the schedule optimizer, and communicate results to the user. All interactions must be performed via the defined tool calls."
    },
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Can you produce a tentative schedule for our new hybrid pilot course CS 599 \u2013 Advanced Topics in AI for Fall 2025? It needs a classroom that can hold 30 students and a virtual link, meeting twice a week for 1.5\u202fhours each."
    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
